snippet.textDisplay: I’m not a fan of this group because of their songs that don’t suit my taste, but I’m amazed at how talented they are. all the hype in them is very fair and well deserved and it doesn't look like they are rookies. and they are all on the same dance level. none stands out in my eyes, but that’s not bad, on the contrary. it means that they all dance very well equally. and their choreographies are always very well executed and so satisfying to watch.
